            | 
            "pointTo: only tests if objRep is in the world,
             but if it is off-screen, better to remove it, so pointTo: will
             summon it. -- dmu 6/1"

            objRep isInWorld  &&  [objRep world = world] ifTrue: [
              |w. can. bb|
              w: objRep world.
              can: w winCanvasForHand: aHand.
              bb: can boundingBoxInWorld.
